        {
            "title": "舜宇附屬擬認購歌爾股份旗下公司逾33%股權",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">舜宇光學(02382)公布，旗下公司與深圳A股歌爾股份訂立諒解備忘錄，雙方同意進一步磋商，舜宇旗下寧波奧來入股歌爾股份旗下歌爾光學33.33的股權。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"舜宇光學官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/02382-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"舜宇光學官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/02382-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">舜宇光學官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據諒解備忘錄，訂約方同意進一步磋商，以訂立最終協議，主要條款包括當重組完成後，寧波奧來以其持有的上海奧來的全部股權作價出資，認購歌爾光學的股權；認購事項完成後，寧波奧來將持有歌爾光學股權約33.33%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公布稱，歌爾股份於深圳證券交易所上市(002241.SZ)，主要在中國從事消費及汽車電子行業精密零組件及智能硬件的研發、製造及銷售。歌爾光學專注於高精度光學相關領域，尤其在光波導組件方面，並具有廣泛的客戶群。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">寧波奧來是舜宇浙江光學的全資附屬公司，舜宇浙江光學是舜宇光學的全資附屬公司。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">舜宇光學表示，倘落實認購事項，將促進上海奧來與歌爾光學的優勢互補，增強在光波導及其他晶圓級微納光學器件的核心競爭力。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15197144-%e8%88%9c%e5%ae%87%e9%99%84%e5%b1%ac%e6%93%ac%e8%aa%8d%e8%b3%bc%e6%ad%8c%e7%88%be%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%bd%e6%97%97%e4%b8%8b%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8%e9%80%be33%e8%82%a1%e6%ac%8a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-22 17:50:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "創新奇智半年經調整虧損收窄逾82%  變更招股集資用途",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創新奇智(02121)公布，截至6月30日止半年度，經調整淨虧損668.1萬元，按年收窄82.14%，不派中期息。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"公司年報\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250515_fi_02121_web_fb.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"公司年報\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250515_fi_02121_web_fb.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">公司年報</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內虧損6051.3萬元，按年跌67.21%，收入6.99億元，按年升22.26%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">毛利率升1.2個百分點至35%，經營活動所用現金淨額849萬元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司稱，年度內一家附屬公司存在商業訴訟，該附屬公司總額1130萬元的銀行存款，及其於兩家附屬公司的權益已被凍結，目前訴訟仍在進行中。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司公布變更招股集資用途，原擬用於提升商業化能力的875萬元，重新分配至營運資金及一般公司用途；原擬用於加強內部系統及提升信息基礎設施的2024萬元，重新分配至提升研發能力。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15196943-%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e5%a5%87%e6%99%ba%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e7%b6%93%e8%aa%bf%e6%95%b4%e8%99%a7%e6%90%8d%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84%e9%80%be82-%e8%ae%8a%e6%9b%b4%e6%8b%9b%e8%82%a1%e9%9b%86%e8%b3%87%e7%94%a8",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/02121-2024.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-22 17:15:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股收升234點晶片股搶鏡   科指全周升近1.9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股收升234點，晶片股午後升幅擴大，消費股也向上，電動車股向好，恒生科技指數一周累升近1.9%，恒指累升69點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日報25339，升234點或0.93%，今早開升100點或0.4%，報25205點，最高見25287，升183點或0.73%，為半日高位，隨即窄幅波動，最低見25140，升36點或0.14%，為半日低位。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"李寧門店\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240624_FI_source-bp_02331-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"李寧門店\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240624_FI_source-bp_02331-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">李寧門店</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/bplib_20230705-135716_source-web_00992_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/bplib_20230705-135716_source-web_00992_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"李寧門店\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240624_FI_source-bp_02331-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">李寧門店</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/bplib_20230705-135716_source-web_00992_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日報5647點，升149點或2.71%，今早開升54或0.99%，報5553點，</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日報9079，升105點或1.17%，今早開升50點或0.56%，報9024點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指全日報25354，升245點或0.98%，高水15點 ; 科指期貨報5639，升142點或2.58%，低水9點 ; 國指期貨報9082，升104點或1.16%，高水2點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市現成交2855.84億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指一周累升69點或0.27% ; 科指一周累升104點或1.88% ; 國指一周升40點或0.44%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股午後顯著向上，支持港股，內地晶片股破頂。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">晶片股揚升，A股晶片股也造好，中芯(00981)升10.06%，報56.9元，為表現最佳藍籌股，貢獻恒指36點 ; 華虹半導體(01347)急升17.85%，報56元 ; 上海復旦(01385)升6.36%，報31.76元 ; ASMPT(00522)升5.53%，報69.7元。科技媒體The Information引述知情人士稱，輝達(Nvidia)叫停H20晶片生產，H20是輝達專為中國市場設計的晶片。市場再炒作晶片自主，此外Deepseek升級亦惹憧憬。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)升1.99%，報118元，貢獻恒指38點 ; 小米(01810)升2.34%，報52.55元，貢獻恒指34點，兩股與中芯同是大市支持主力。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">李寧(02331)全日升8.78%，報19.7元，升幅居藍籌股第二位，雖然半年盈利倒退兼減派息，惟業績仍優於市場預期，摩根士丹利指上半年核心經營溢利較該行預測高21%。同類股份安踏(02020)升3.12%，報102.5元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">食品股也升，海倫司(09869)升3.76%，報1.38元 ; 滬上阿姨(02589)揚5.08%，報155.2元; 綠茶集團(06831)升2.75%，報7.48% ; 蜜雪集團(02097)升2.67%，報477.4元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">同屬消費股的名創優品(09896)半日飛升18.28%，報46.2元，上半年純利倒退22.6%，但增加派息，刺激隔晚(21日)美股(MNSO.US)收升6.4%至22.17美元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"李寧門店\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240624_FI_source-bp_02331-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"李寧門店\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240624_FI_source-bp_02331-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">李寧門店</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">電動車股升幅擴大，小鵬汽車(09868)飆13.6%，報91.9元，大股東增持股份310萬股，均價80.49元。零跑(09863)升1.43%，報71元，其餘電動車股向好，比亞迪(01211)升2.6%，報114.3元 ; 理想汽車(02015)升1.37%，報92.25元。從事解決方案的地平綫機器人(09660)午後升，收升4.79%，報7.66元，成交入20大。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">聯想集團(00992)午後挫，收跌2.19%，報10.73元，為表現最差藍籌股。     </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中石化(00386)半年盈利跌35.9%，至237.5億元人幣，中期息減40%至8.8分，全日跌1.78%，報4.41元，跌幅藍籌股中居第二位。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/bplib_20230705-135716_source-web_00992_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/bplib_20230705-135716_source-web_00992_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：聯想官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">嗶哩嗶哩(09626)全日跌6.15%，報184.7元，最低見181.5元，跌7.77%，公司次季業績勝預期，惟下半年遊戲收入指引遜預期。騰訊(00700)升1.18%，報600元，突破600元關  ;美團(03690)升1.11%，報118.4元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中興通訊(00763)升15.13%，報36.06元，成交入20大。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15196892-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%87234%e9%bb%9e%e6%99%b6%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e6%90%b6%e9%8f%a1-%e7%a7%91%e6%8c%87%e5%85%a8%e5%91%a8%e5%8d%87%e8%bf%911-9",
